{"tid":776504,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"入「魔」快樂嗎？普巴：講真話會被罰","createTime":"2018-08-12T06:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T07:12:51.000Z","uid":153600,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"44efe487bed47a1fe7aa6b8015a38d9dd0b9e757","tid":776504,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:48:32.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=JuWwQ8HBR92R197b3UYfJl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=aceabb6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯中場保羅普巴一直被傳跟領隊摩連奴不和，他日前就表示，要是自己坦白所有事情，肯定會被球會處罰。<br />\n<br />\n在周五首輪英超，保羅普巴（Paul Pogba）以隊長身份在上半場射入12碼，帶領曼聯以2:1擊敗李斯特城，新球季旗開得勝。摩連奴賽後大讚這名中場主將的演出，更以怪物去形容。<br />\n<br />\n表現比上季大躍進，普巴說：「你說的真普巴是甚麼意思？要是你享受現在所做的事，就會交出你的所有。要是你不快樂，就不能夠踢出最好的足球。」不過，當被問及現時在紅魔快不快樂時，他似乎若有所指：「有很多事情我不能說，否則將會被罰。」<br />\n<br />\n25歲的普巴在上仗成為隊長後，多謝的人是助教卡域克及麥堅拿，而不是摩佬：「戴起隊長臂章令我自豪，是夢想成真。卡域克與麥堅拿都跟我說，曼聯是一家大球會，人們如何看重我。當你感到舒適、獲得信任，頭腦就會更清晰。」"},{"pid":"91d2ff939d474eb7534dfde6dfac9556890d381c","tid":776504,"uid":67225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:53:18.000Z","msg":"反了"},{"pid":"97208da5beecd1c58c3634279b595fe3021a624b","tid":776504,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:54:58.000Z","msg":"唔洗捉鬼了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n摩佬又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e003d8d4b7df9ee028fbcfcbb53602fda2ca0d41","tid":776504,"uid":52939,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:00:13.000Z","msg":"妹妹真係養唔撚熟"},{"pid":"7dcf72e476bea9dc301147369bc708accaf9a717","tid":776504,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:02:20.000Z","msg":"25"},{"pid":"d6f23c58a864ac80128888a2c6f30813f27136ce","tid":776504,"uid":7940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"摩佬：違約金fat fat la <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c918d60c1b8e021c173cd27c35452e4690db8f1e","tid":776504,"uid":161731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:10:43.000Z","msg":"普巴好有魔性 好撚型"},{"pid":"55e18491d88dd52347a3d41c51e158a5c6622ed7","tid":776504,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:12:51.000Z","msg":"魔性澎湃"}]}